data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that sits on just under 3 acres of tranquility. The spacious interior boasts a large kitchen, inviting living room, and a large rec room, creating an ideal space for entertaining family and guests. Step outside to enjoy gatherings on the covered patio. With 2 cleared acres, the property offers an excellent option for horses or other animals. Embrace the perfect blend of comfort and outdoor possibilities in this delightful home
